  <Dialog id="0" name="MSG_000_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 1 0 0}What do you think, Yamagishi? Do you sense anything?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="1" name="MSG_001_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 6 3 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 2 0 0}No...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="2" name="MSG_002_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 0 201 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 0 0 0 3 0 0}......[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="3" name="MSG_003_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 3 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 4 0 0}By refusing to speak, you're only hurting yourself.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 3 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 5 0 0}We aren't trying to keep you hostage; we just want to avoid unnecessary confrontation.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="4" name="MSG_004_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 0 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 6 0 0}...How's Chidori?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="5" name="MSG_005_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0004"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 4 0 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 7 0 0}You're back again? Why are you so hung up on her, Junpei?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="6" name="MSG_006_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 3 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 8 0 0}Did she say anything?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="7" name="MSG_007_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 9 0 0}...Not a word.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="8" name="MSG_008_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 2 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 10 0 0}Let me talk to her.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="9" name="MSG_009_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 11 0 0}Iori... You're getting really emotionally invested in this.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 12 0 0}Is everything all right?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="10" name="MSG_010_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 2 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 13 0 0}Well...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 2 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 14 0 0}I know she attacked me, but...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 2 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 15 0 0}I don't know, I just can't get her out of my head! Please, let me do this![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="11" name="MSG_011_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 6 4 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 16 0 0}Junpei-kun...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="12" name="MSG_012_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0004"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 4 0 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 17 0 0}Geez...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="13" name="MSG_013_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 18 0 0}Mmm... Desperate times call for desperate measures, I suppose. All right, see if you can get through to her.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="14" name="MSG_014_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 0 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 19 0 0}Got it![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="15" name="MSG_015_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 3 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 20 0 0}You okay?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="16" name="MSG_016_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 3 201 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 0 0 0 21 0 0}......[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="17" name="MSG_017_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 3 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 22 0 0}I'm glad they let you keep your sketchbook...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 3 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 23 0 0}Wow, you're still drawing pictures, even in the hospital?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 3 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 24 0 0}You really do like to draw, huh?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="18" name="MSG_018_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 3 201 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 0 0 0 25 0 0}......[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 3 201 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 26 0 0}...It doesn't matter.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="19" name="MSG_019_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 6 4 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 27 0 0}She spoke to him...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="20" name="MSG_020_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 3 201 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 28 0 0}Only I can understand my drawings...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="21" name="MSG_021_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 29 0 0}Wait... Chidori!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 30 0 0}Your arm! It's bleeding![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="22" name="MSG_022_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0004"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 4 2 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 31 0 0}Tch... Not again![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="23" name="MSG_022_5_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0004"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 4 2 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 32 0 0}Yamagishi, get the doctor![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="24" name="MSG_023_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 6 4 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 33 0 0}R-Right![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="25" name="MSG_024_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 34 0 0}What happened!? Why're you bleeding!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="26" name="MSG_025_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0004"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 4 2 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 35 0 0}She does it to herself.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0004"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 4 2 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 36 0 0}I thought I took all the sharp objects in here.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="27" name="MSG_026_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 37 0 0}She did this to herself...!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="28" name="MSG_027_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 3 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 38 0 0}...Apparently, we can't leave her unattended for even a moment.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 3 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 39 0 0}But at the very least, she seems to heal at an astonishing rate...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="29" name="MSG_028_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 3 201 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 40 0 0}Let go of me![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="30" name="MSG_029_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 41 0 0}Then, that cut on your hand back at the station... You did that to yourself!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="31" name="MSG_030_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 3 201 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 42 0 0}...I never asked for you to worry about me.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 3 201 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 43 0 0}You were the one who jumped to conclusions.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="32" name="MSG_031_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 3 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 44 0 0}Well, I want you to stop.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="33" name="MSG_032_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 3 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 45 0 0}You can't be doing that...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 3 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 46 0 0}I'm not just saying this because I'm worried about you.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 3 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 47 0 0}I don't want to see you hurting yourself... Alright?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="34" name="MSG_033_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 3 201 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 0 0 0 48 0 0}......[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="35" name="MSG_034_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 49 0 0}The doctor will be here soon. You should head back.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="36" name="MSG_035_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 3 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 50 0 0}...Right.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="37" name="MSG_036_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 51 0 0}...So, you seem to have found your voice.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
